{
  "arquivo": "ca02_13",
  "total": 18,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(After drifting on the waves for a while,\\n we returned the float\\n and headed back to the sandy beach.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That just felt so good.\\nIt was an experience that's hard to come by.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Yes, it felt like we became a part of nature.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But in the end, I couldn't kiss her...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Wait! Come to think of it,\\n maybe the others really were watching us.\\n It wasn't the right time for that, right?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Uwaah?!\\nWh-what is it, Miku?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Why are you so startled?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No reason, really...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Big bro!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "H-hey, welcome back.\\nDid you have fun?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, we went out pretty far,\\nand Yotsuba-san was so fast,\\nit almost shocked me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well, I'm glad you enjoyed it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Um, how about a short break?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, swimming is quite exhausting. Let's take a break.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "There was a shop over there.\\nI'm wondering what drink I should get...\\nMatcha soda would be perfect...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(A break, huh.\\n What should I do...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}